ptdb.common.dto

Class DBGraphSearchCriteria

  • java.lang.Object
    • ptdb.common.dto.DBGraphSearchCriteria

  • public class DBGraphSearchCriteria
extends java.lang.Object
    The DTO (data transfer object) that all the search criteria input by the user, for the graph searching through the XML database.

    It is constructed by the GUI layer class to pass the search criteria for graph DB search to the database layer.

    Since:
    Ptolemy II 10.0
